This weekend's show also saw singer Septimus Prime win the judges around and reveal his secret health battle. 
The teenager suffers from a mystery heart ailment which makes him pass out without warning. 
The 19-year-old Londoner, who wowed judges last night with his performance of Justin Bieber’s Love Yourself , says he was once hospitalised after collapsing onstage — one of many such scares throughout his life — and he fears the same thing could happen on The Voice.
